#-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
#
#  EUROBRAILLE DISPLAY TABLE
#
#  This character mapping of 6-dot braille is widely being
#  used in german speaking parts of europe.
#
#  Version 2009-11-19
#  christian.waldvogel@sbszh.ch
