lowercase \x04E9 1269    CYRILLIC LETTER Ãž Ó©
lowercase \x04A1 1469    CYRILLIC LETTER q Ò¡
lowercase \x0493 124569  CYRILLIC LETTER É£ Ò
lowercase \x04AB 349     CYRILLIC LETTER Îž Ò«
lowercase \x0499 3469    CYRILLIC LETTER Ã° Ò
lowercase \x04BB 12369   CYRILLIC LETTER h Ò»
lowercase \x04AF 134569  CYRILLIC LETTER y Ò¯
lowercase \x04A3 14569   CYRILLIC LETTER Å Ò£

