always @ 4-1
always \\ 4-1256
always | 456-1256
always \s-\s 36
always ..." 5-5-5-356
always âŠ 5-5-5
always ... 5-5-5
always ...' 5-5-5-356-3
repeated .... 0
repeated ____ 6-36-36-3
repeated ---- 36
always .\s.\s." 3-3-3-356
