display \x00ad 367      # 173 Â­    SOFT HYPHEN
display \x00ab 1267     # 171 Â«    LEFT-POINTING DOUBLE ANGLE QUOTATION MARK
display \x00bb 3457     # 187 Â»    RIGHT-POINTING DOUBLE ANGLE QUOTATION MARK
